The '''Dorat villa''' was the home of [[Chel Dorat|Chel]] and [[Preela Dorat]]. It was situated in the south western part of [[Graleca]] city on [[Jerrilek]]. [[D3S]] and other [[Droid/Legends|droids]] also resided in the house. The house was situated by a bay.<ref name="AJ4">{{JournalCite|4|Loyalties}}</ref>

